-- Pimco's Gross:'New Neutral' real policy rate will be close to 0 pct  
-- 
-- Thu Jun 05, 2014 08:00AM EDT
-- None



June 5 (Reuters) - Bill Gross, manager of the world's largest bond fund at Pimco, said Thursday the firm believes the 'new neutral' real policy rate will be close to 0 percent as opposed to 2-3 percent in prior decades.

